  <h1><b><i><u>cybersecurity</u></i></b></h1>
  <hr>
  <h1>Introduction</h1>

  <p>
    In today's digitally interconnected world, cybersecurity has emerged as a critical issue that affects individuals,
    corporations, and governments alike. As technology becomes more deeply integrated into our daily lives — from
    communication and commerce to healthcare and education — the need to protect digital systems and data becomes
    increasingly urgent.

    Cyberattacks are no longer rare incidents limited to IT departments; they are real, widespread threats that can
    cripple infrastructure, steal identities, and cost millions. As such, understanding cybersecurity is not just an
    option — it’s a necessity in the modern age.
  </p>
  <img src="img/cyber.jpg" width="300px" height="400px" title="cys">
